IN MONTE CARLO, MONACO The stage is set for the IAAF awards gala in Monte Carlo in Monaco where the Male and Female Athletes of the year will be known. Kenya's Eliud Kipchoge, the world marathon record holder, is likely to bag the Male award while compatriot and steeplechase queen Beatrice Chepkoech is in contention for the Female award. Athletes from all corners of the world have graced the awards as seen below:               Every journalist in the room received a copy that Kipchoge patiently autographed.